title: Digital Elevation Model Phase 2
description:
Phase2 (2019 - 2023) Statewide LiDAR-derived Digital Elevation Model.

This is the KyFromAbove Phase2 collection and provides access to a 2 Foot Digital Elevation Model (DEM) for Kentucky. Data will be added to this dataset as it becomes available through the KyFromAbove Program. LiDAR was collected at Quality Level 2 or better from 2019 - 2023 for KYAPED project areas while no snow was on the ground and rivers were at or below normal levels.
